法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">const <em>state</em> = <em>track</em>.readyState</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"值","title":"值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>它采用以下值之一：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>\"live\"</code>表示输入已连接，并尽最大努力提供实时数据。 在这种情况下，可以使用<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack/enabled\"><code>MediaStreamTrack.enabled</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>属性打开或关闭数据输出。</li>\n <li><code>\"ended\"</code>表示输入不再提供任何数据，也永远不会提供新数据。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"技术指标","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\" style=\"height: 49px; width: 1000px;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediastreamtrack-readystate\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Media Capture and Streams<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">MediaStreamTrack.readyState</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Candidate Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial specification.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaStreamTrack.readyState","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack/readyState/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"看看别的","title":"看看别的","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Media_Streams_API\">Media Stream API</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebRTC_API\">WebRTC</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack/ended_event\"><code>MediaStreamTrack.onended</code> <small>(en-US)</s